1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:57,340 --> 00:02:00,740
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

3
00:02:00,740 --> 00:02:01,580
Ma'am,

4
00:02:01,780 --> 00:02:02,820
we want the overnight stay.

5
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:04,980
I'm sorry.

6
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,380
We have inspections these few days.

7
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,380
No overnight stays.

8
00:02:07,700 --> 00:02:08,540
Wait, no...

9
00:02:08,540 --> 00:02:09,900
Fine, let's go.

10
00:02:11,100 --> 00:02:11,940
I'm sorry.

11
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:13,140
Next time you guys come,

12
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:14,620
I'll give you an extra hour for free.

13
00:02:15,340 --> 00:02:16,480
You should've told us.

14
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,380
I'm sorry.

15
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:18,220
What inspection...

16
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:24,900
I'm sorry.

17
00:02:24,900 --> 00:02:26,180
We're closed for today.

18
00:02:28,180 --> 00:02:29,020
Songge.

19
00:02:47,660 --> 00:02:48,700
You're finally back.

20
00:02:51,940 --> 00:02:52,780
I'm back.

21
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:58,180
Since you're out,
did you go see your parents?

22
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,340
I did.

23
00:03:06,060 --> 00:03:07,180
But they...

24
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:10,740
They don't want me anymore.

25
00:03:18,470 --> 00:03:19,580
I don't have a home anymore.

26
00:03:22,210 --> 00:03:23,380
We don't have a home anymore.

27
00:03:54,060 --> 00:03:57,940
=Episode 17=
(The Countermove)

28
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,500
Hongbing.

29
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:16,260
Dad.

30
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:17,420
Mom.

31
00:04:18,220 --> 00:04:19,820
Why did you sleep here all night again?

32
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:22,060
I only meant to stay a while,

33
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,260
but I accidentally fell asleep.

34
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,660
Chen Hongbing.

35
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:26,540
It's time.

36
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,220
Look at you.

37
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,300
You're dressed so lightly.

38
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:40,860
Mom,

39
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:42,620
are you and Dad okay?

40
00:04:42,620 --> 00:04:43,580
We're fine.

41
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,220
But the weather's getting cold now.

42
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,540
Don't you dare stay here

43
00:04:47,540 --> 00:04:48,660
and sleep all night again.

44
00:04:48,660 --> 00:04:49,500
You'll get sick.

45
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:51,260
I just missed you guys.

46
00:04:52,020 --> 00:04:53,220
Dad won't let me come home,

47
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:55,140
so I can only come see you here.

48
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:00,020
Silly child.

49
00:05:00,020 --> 00:05:00,860
It's okay.

50
00:05:01,380 --> 00:05:02,380
I'll find a chance

51
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,660
to talk to your father later.

52
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:06,980
Mom,

53
00:05:06,980 --> 00:05:08,300
don't upset Dad because of me.

54
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:10,220
It's fine.

55
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:11,060
Don't worry about it.

56
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:11,940
Go on back.

57
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,060
Get some sleep.

58
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:15,060
I'll head to work now.

59
00:05:15,420 --> 00:05:16,260
Go on.

60
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:17,340
Make sure you rest.

61
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:18,740
You look terrible.

62
00:05:18,740 --> 00:05:19,580
Okay.

63
00:05:19,850 --> 00:05:21,100
Drive carefully on the way back.

64
00:05:22,060 --> 00:05:23,220
Take care, Mom.

65
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:40,860
(People's Public Security)

66
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:43,900
Hongbing.

67
00:05:45,460 --> 00:05:46,300
Liang,

68
00:05:46,700 --> 00:05:47,540
did they

69
00:05:47,620 --> 00:05:48,620
let you out early?

70
00:05:49,780 --> 00:05:50,620
While I was inside,

71
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:51,860
I kept coughing.

72
00:05:51,860 --> 00:05:53,180
Later, I was diagnosed

73
00:05:53,180 --> 00:05:54,060
with COPD.

74
00:05:54,060 --> 00:05:55,420
So I'm out on medical parole.

75
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,780
At our age,

76
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:00,140
it's always one ailment or another.

77
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:00,980
True.

78
00:06:00,980 --> 00:06:02,290
The body's aging. Needs some repairs.

79
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:03,300
Repairs, huh?

80
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:05,210
You didn't even tell me you're back.

81
00:06:05,210 --> 00:06:06,060
I just wanted

82
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:07,340
to give you a surprise.

83
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:08,910
And I wanted
to register here while I'm at it.

84
00:06:09,170 --> 00:06:10,030
Done yet?

85
00:06:10,030 --> 00:06:10,890
Not yet.

86
00:06:10,890 --> 00:06:11,820
Come on, I'll go with you.

87
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:12,770
- Alright.
- Let's go.

88
00:06:12,770 --> 00:06:13,620
Hongbing.

89
00:06:14,500 --> 00:06:16,100
(Ding Yue Clinic)

90
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:18,060
For this medicine,

91
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:20,140
take one pill each
at breakfast and dinner.

92
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:20,990
Take it with food.

93
00:06:20,990 --> 00:06:22,090
Never on an empty stomach.

94
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:22,940
If you still feel

95
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:23,800
upset in your stomach,

96
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,820
eat a mantou

97
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,790
or have some soda

98
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:26,820
to settle it.

99
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:27,860
Remember to take it on time.

100
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:28,860
Thank you, Dr. Ding.

101
00:06:28,860 --> 00:06:29,700
No problem.

102
00:06:38,940 --> 00:06:39,780
Mrs. Chen.

103
00:06:40,340 --> 00:06:41,340
Mr. Yang,

104
00:06:41,780 --> 00:06:42,620
how do you have time

105
00:06:42,620 --> 00:06:43,660
to visit us today?

106
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,500
Well...

107
00:06:44,820 --> 00:06:45,900
Give me an injection.

108
00:06:45,900 --> 00:06:47,140
You're a cadre at the mine.

109
00:06:47,140 --> 00:06:48,810
You should go to
the Workers' Hospital for an injection.

110
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:50,220
The Workers' Hospital is too crowded.

111
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:51,100
You have to wait in line.

112
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:51,980
Besides, if I run into someone I know,

113
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:52,940
we'll be chatting forever.

114
00:06:52,940 --> 00:06:54,210
Just help me out and do it here.

115
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:56,420
What kind of injection?

116
00:06:56,540 --> 00:06:57,380
In the butt.

117
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:01,540
Go and wait.

118
00:07:04,900 --> 00:07:06,500
(Ceftriaxone for Injection)

119
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:14,620
Mrs. Chen.

120
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,410
Hongbing still hasn't
let Hui into the house?

121
00:07:17,140 --> 00:07:18,340
Stop gossiping here.

122
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:20,060
Well, isn't there an old saying?

123
00:07:20,060 --> 00:07:22,660
"A lazy man marries a beauty,
but a good man gets a bad wife."

124
00:07:23,260 --> 00:07:24,940
Hui is such a good kid,

125
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,710
so how did he end up
with someone so sickly?

126
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:30,940
Does it hurt?

127
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:32,530
It's okay, I can handle it.
It doesn't hurt.

128
00:07:32,540 --> 00:07:33,800
I'm not talking about your butt.

129
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,460
I mean, does it hurt when you urinate?

130
00:07:37,340 --> 00:07:38,620
So you know?

131
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,940
I just don't understand.

132
00:07:39,940 --> 00:07:41,340
You're married to Xiaoyun,

133
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:42,940
and that is already a blessing
from your ancestors.

134
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:44,410
Yet, you still go out and mess around.

135
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,100
You've caught a filthy disease.

136
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:47,450
So are you satisfied and happy now?

137
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:48,300
That's enough, Mrs. Chen.

138
00:07:48,300 --> 00:07:49,380
Keep your voice down.

139
00:07:49,380 --> 00:07:50,540
You have to keep it a secret.

140
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,060
If Xiaoyun finds out, I'm finished.

141
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,780
Now, you care about secrets, huh?

142
00:07:56,060 --> 00:07:57,940
You're pushing that in a bit too fast.

143
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:00,220
All done.

144
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,660
Have you taken your insulin?

145
00:08:09,820 --> 00:08:11,580
Didn't I tell you
to take it before meals?

146
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:13,660
I was actually just thinking about it.

147
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:15,620
Please don't forget.

148
00:08:15,940 --> 00:08:17,460
I can't forget.

149
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:18,740
It's only been a few days.

150
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:19,860
I'm not used to it yet.

151
00:08:20,820 --> 00:08:22,820
Taking a shot before every meal...

152
00:08:22,820 --> 00:08:24,380
What has my life become?

153
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:25,820
You have to get used to it.

154
00:08:25,820 --> 00:08:26,910
You can't miss a single day.

155
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,420
Got it.

156
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:33,620
You don't need my help?

157
00:08:34,100 --> 00:08:35,180
No.

158
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,180
What do you call this?

159
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:40,620
This

160
00:08:40,620 --> 00:08:42,220
is self-torture.

161
00:08:44,180 --> 00:08:45,610
I want to talk to you about something.

162
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:47,980
Go ahead.

163
00:08:48,060 --> 00:08:49,100
This morning,

164
00:08:49,100 --> 00:08:50,380
didn't we run into Hui?

165
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:53,220
He told me

166
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:55,060
that he misses us.

167
00:08:57,420 --> 00:08:58,310
You should have seen

168
00:08:58,310 --> 00:08:59,640
the look in his eyes.

169
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,060
It was heartbreaking.

170
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,180
Do you remember

171
00:09:03,540 --> 00:09:04,820
when he was eight years old?

172
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,700
That time when you went to the mine
to bust a gambling ring,

173
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:09,180
and you were beaten
and got a concussion?

174
00:09:09,180 --> 00:09:10,780
You were in the hospital for a few days.

175
00:09:11,060 --> 00:09:13,740
He stayed by your bedside
the whole time.

176
00:09:13,740 --> 00:09:14,740
The way he looked today

177
00:09:14,740 --> 00:09:16,220
was exactly the same as back then.

178
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,100
Anyway, I don't care.

179
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:23,820
This is my home too,

180
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:25,420
and Hui is my son.

181
00:09:25,420 --> 00:09:27,380
I want him to bring Songge

182
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,860
over for a family reunion dinner.

183
00:09:32,100 --> 00:09:32,940
Are you finished?

184
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,380
Let's eat.

185
00:09:39,420 --> 00:09:41,260
If you don't give me an answer, don't eat.

186
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:44,860
Did I say I didn't agree?

187
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,020
So that means

188
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:49,020
you agree?

189
00:09:51,700 --> 00:09:52,540
You decide.

190
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:56,540
Here, this is yours.

191
00:09:57,060 --> 00:09:58,580
These two dishes are for you.

192
00:09:58,580 --> 00:09:59,420
Eat up.

193
00:10:00,020 --> 00:10:01,060
Come on.

194
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,340
So am I a monk now?

195
00:10:04,340 --> 00:10:05,860
There's not a single piece of meat.

196
00:10:05,860 --> 00:10:07,140
This is for your health.

197
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:08,780
Try some.

198
00:10:09,420 --> 00:10:10,260
Seriously.

199
00:10:12,020 --> 00:10:12,860
Your drink.

200
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:18,050
Hello, Yingxiong Internet Cafe.

201
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:19,900
Songge, it's Mrs. Chen.

202
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:21,140
Mrs. Chen.

203
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,580
What's up, Mrs. Chen?

204
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:24,700
Nothing much.

205
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:26,080
I just wanted to tell you

206
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:27,050
that this weekend,

207
00:10:27,050 --> 00:10:28,680
you and Hui should come over for dinner.

208
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,100
So,

209
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:32,700
did Mr. Chen agree?

210
00:10:33,940 --> 00:10:34,960
He didn't say yes,

211
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,900
but he didn't say no, either.

212
00:10:37,860 --> 00:10:38,700
Great.

213
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,660
I'll go tell Chen Hui.

214
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:41,860
He'll be so happy.

215
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:43,860
We really miss home.

216
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,700
We miss you guys.

217
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:47,300
Songge,

218
00:10:47,740 --> 00:10:48,940
I was being foolish before.

219
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,340
I didn't want

220
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:51,900
you and Hui to be together.

221
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:53,900
Now that things are hard,

222
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:55,260
I can see

223
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:57,460
that family should
always stick together.

224
00:10:58,780 --> 00:10:59,940
Don't worry, Mrs. Chen.

225
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:01,220
We'll go back this weekend.

226
00:11:02,980 --> 00:11:03,860
I'm hanging up now.

227
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:05,060
Goodbye, Mrs. Chen.

228
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:06,620
Songge.

229
00:11:06,980 --> 00:11:07,820
What is it?

230
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:09,060
I have good news.

231
00:11:09,370 --> 00:11:10,280
Just now,

232
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,300
Mrs. Chen called me.

233
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:13,390
She wants us to go back
to Fengyang for dinner on Sunday.

234
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:16,020
Really?

235
00:11:17,420 --> 00:11:18,260
That's great.

236
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:19,500
That's wonderful.

237
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:21,200
Should we prepare

238
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,300
something to bring over?

239
00:11:22,300 --> 00:11:23,300
Let's go buy it now.

240
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,540
Come on, let's go right now.

241
00:11:28,940 --> 00:11:30,060
Growing up,

242
00:11:30,060 --> 00:11:31,980
I've never seen Mrs. Chen wear jewelry.

243
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:33,460
I wonder if she'll like it.

244
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,310
That's because she could
never bring herself to buy it.

245
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:37,620
When she sees this,

246
00:11:37,620 --> 00:11:38,780
she'll absolutely love it.

247
00:11:41,340 --> 00:11:42,210
So, what do you think

248
00:11:42,210 --> 00:11:43,980
of these shoes I bought for Mr. Chen?

249
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:45,900
I think they're great.

250
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:46,940
They seem

251
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:47,900
really comfortable.

252
00:11:55,500 --> 00:11:56,340
What's this?

253
00:11:56,940 --> 00:11:58,100
I bought it for you.

254
00:11:58,100 --> 00:11:59,180
To keep you safe.

255
00:11:59,180 --> 00:12:00,110
It's pretty, isn't it?

256
00:12:00,700 --> 00:12:01,540
Yes.

257
00:12:16,060 --> 00:12:17,100
Are you ready?

258
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:22,060
Let's go in then.

259
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:38,820
Mr. Chen, Mrs. Chen,

260
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:39,860
we're back.

261
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:00,620
Time to eat.

262
00:13:01,140 --> 00:13:01,980
Hongbing,

263
00:13:01,980 --> 00:13:03,300
go take your insulin first.

264
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:04,740
Okay.

265
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:13,500
Dad,

266
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:14,860
use this one.

267
00:13:15,140 --> 00:13:15,980
This is better.

268
00:13:28,540 --> 00:13:29,410
Hui,

269
00:13:29,410 --> 00:13:30,820
you can't let your dad use that.

270
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:32,420
Why not?

271
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:33,900
With insulin,

272
00:13:33,900 --> 00:13:35,420
every brand has a different dosage.

273
00:13:35,420 --> 00:13:37,720
If you switch brands,
the dosage has to be readjusted.

274
00:13:37,730 --> 00:13:38,940
Mom, you're the professional after all.

275
00:13:40,540 --> 00:13:41,500
This is a big brand.

276
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:42,940
It must have cost a lot.

277
00:13:43,580 --> 00:13:44,420
Hongbing,

278
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:45,780
look at this. Your son's great,

279
00:13:45,780 --> 00:13:46,620
no?

280
00:13:58,140 --> 00:13:59,420
Let's eat.

281
00:14:00,900 --> 00:14:01,820
Yes, let's eat.

282
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:02,980
Hui, come sit down.

283
00:14:02,980 --> 00:14:03,850
Songge, you sit too.

284
00:14:03,850 --> 00:14:04,700
Let's eat.

285
00:14:13,380 --> 00:14:14,220
Hey,

286
00:14:14,860 --> 00:14:16,460
take some time next week when you're off

287
00:14:16,460 --> 00:14:17,320
to adjust the dosage

288
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,740
for the new one Hui bought.

289
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:20,580
Stop using those old syringes.

290
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:22,100
It makes me nervous just watching.

291
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:27,420
Mr. Chen,

292
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:29,420
try this braised lamb.

293
00:14:29,980 --> 00:14:31,020
I made it today.

294
00:14:37,180 --> 00:14:38,020
It's delicious.

295
00:14:39,060 --> 00:14:39,900
Come on,

296
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:40,900
you guys eat too.

297
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:51,060
This braised lamb

298
00:14:51,060 --> 00:14:53,020
is your Mr. Chen's favorite dish
in the world.

299
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:54,260
If he says it's good,

300
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,460
then you've already

301
00:14:55,460 --> 00:14:56,460
learned all my secrets.

302
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,740
Hui isn't usually by my side,

303
00:14:58,740 --> 00:14:59,740
and as his mother,

304
00:14:59,740 --> 00:15:01,540
I always worry he's not eating well.

305
00:15:01,540 --> 00:15:02,660
You should make this often

306
00:15:02,660 --> 00:15:03,720
so he can have it more.

307
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:04,690
I will, Mrs. Chen.

308
00:15:04,690 --> 00:15:05,700
Don't worry.

309
00:15:05,700 --> 00:15:06,580
When Hui is with me,

310
00:15:06,580 --> 00:15:07,740
I will treat him well.

311
00:15:09,340 --> 00:15:10,940
In this life of ours,

312
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:12,080
it's all about the children.

313
00:15:12,580 --> 00:15:14,700
As long as you two can live in harmony,

314
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:15,660
this family of ours

315
00:15:15,660 --> 00:15:16,820
will be at its best.

316
00:15:17,620 --> 00:15:18,740
Isn't that right, Hongbing?

317
00:15:23,060 --> 00:15:23,980
Am I right?

318
00:15:23,980 --> 00:15:24,980
Aren't you hungry?

319
00:15:28,180 --> 00:15:29,020
I'm hungry.

320
00:15:29,100 --> 00:15:29,940
Then what?

321
00:15:30,780 --> 00:15:31,620
Let's eat.

322
00:15:31,900 --> 00:15:33,320
Come on, let's eat.

323
00:15:34,020 --> 00:15:34,920
Come here, Hui.

324
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:37,100
Try Songge's cooking.

325
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,300
Thanks, Mom.

326
00:15:38,300 --> 00:15:39,480
Mrs. Chen, you should eat too.

327
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:53,020
No need to see us out.

328
00:15:53,020 --> 00:15:54,110
- It's freezing.
- I'm heading out, Mrs. Chen.

329
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:55,340
Take it slow on the road.

330
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:56,820
Drive carefully.

331
00:15:59,540 --> 00:16:00,380
We're off.

332
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:01,220
Bye-bye.

333
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:19,980
Stop watching.

334
00:16:19,980 --> 00:16:20,820
They're already gone.

335
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,100
Why are you walking alone

336
00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:21,540
on the road late at night?

337
00:17:21,540 --> 00:17:22,420
It's so dangerous.

338
00:17:25,020 --> 00:17:26,820
Where did you come from?

339
00:17:27,940 --> 00:17:28,780
Gansu.

340
00:17:29,260 --> 00:17:30,100
Gansu?

341
00:17:31,700 --> 00:17:32,620
That's so far.

342
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:34,660
You didn't walk

343
00:17:34,660 --> 00:17:35,700
this entire way, right?

344
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:55,060
(Welcome to Xianguling Gas Station)

345
00:17:58,780 --> 00:17:59,620
Boss.

346
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:07,780
(Wanted Poster)

347
00:19:07,540 --> 00:19:08,620
Liang,

348
00:19:08,620 --> 00:19:10,700
you've made some serious progress.

349
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:12,140
You've settled down,

350
00:19:12,140 --> 00:19:13,420
and you've even quit drinking.

351
00:19:13,420 --> 00:19:14,340
Don't underestimate

352
00:19:14,340 --> 00:19:15,740
the time I spent in there.

353
00:19:15,740 --> 00:19:16,580
It improved me

354
00:19:16,580 --> 00:19:17,540
quite a lot.

355
00:19:18,300 --> 00:19:19,150
Otherwise,

356
00:19:19,150 --> 00:19:20,500
wouldn't I still be with you guys,

357
00:19:20,520 --> 00:19:21,460
eating and drinking my life away,

358
00:19:21,460 --> 00:19:22,370
wasting my time?

359
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:25,060
Wasting your time?

360
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,410
Right,

361
00:19:26,410 --> 00:19:27,860
I have some big news for you.

362
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:30,310
The Fengyang Coal Mine
is said to be closing down.

363
00:19:30,460 --> 00:19:31,300
Didn't you guys know?

364
00:19:32,460 --> 00:19:33,330
No way. Is that true?

365
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:34,300
I've heard about it.

366
00:19:34,820 --> 00:19:37,460
Higher-ups are discussing
cutting production and shutting down.

367
00:19:38,820 --> 00:19:40,260
Won't we lose a fortune, then?

368
00:19:40,260 --> 00:19:41,100
Yeah.

369
00:19:42,660 --> 00:19:43,820
Times are evolving,

370
00:19:43,820 --> 00:19:44,980
and humanity is progressing.

371
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:46,380
What are you worried about?

372
00:19:46,380 --> 00:19:47,220
Anyway, this has

373
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:48,460
nothing to do with me.

374
00:19:48,460 --> 00:19:50,430
I'm not running
illegal coal pits anymore.

375
00:19:50,430 --> 00:19:51,540
As long as I don't break the law,

376
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,850
there'll be plenty of good work for me.

377
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:54,950
Alright, come on.

378
00:19:55,180 --> 00:19:56,940
Let's stop talking
about depressing things.

379
00:19:57,540 --> 00:19:58,380
Today,

380
00:19:58,500 --> 00:20:00,220
we, as Liang's childhood friends,

381
00:20:00,220 --> 00:20:01,980
are here to welcome him back.

382
00:20:01,980 --> 00:20:03,180
Let's give Liang a toast.

383
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:04,940
We wish you, Liang,

384
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:07,260
on your future path in life,

385
00:20:07,260 --> 00:20:08,380
smooth sailing

386
00:20:08,380 --> 00:20:09,220
and safety.

387
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:11,370
Fill it up.

388
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:12,220
I'd better not drink.

389
00:20:12,220 --> 00:20:13,580
You must!

390
00:20:13,580 --> 00:20:14,540
You must drink today.

391
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:15,410
Exactly.

392
00:20:15,410 --> 00:20:16,620
Alright, just a little bit.

393
00:20:16,780 --> 00:20:17,690
- Okay.
- Fill it up!

394
00:20:17,690 --> 00:20:18,940
- Fine. Come on.
- Cheers.

395
00:20:19,300 --> 00:20:21,100
Let's all have one together.

396
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:22,980
Abide by the law.

397
00:20:23,520 --> 00:20:24,900
Act courageously for a just cause.

398
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,300
Fine, then if you fall
into the river later,

399
00:20:26,300 --> 00:20:27,300
I'll go rescue you.

400
00:20:27,300 --> 00:20:28,140
You talk too much.

401
00:20:29,180 --> 00:20:30,780
Thank you.

402
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:35,140
You said you wouldn't drink,
yet you finished so much.

403
00:20:35,140 --> 00:20:36,220
I'm just happy!

404
00:20:36,220 --> 00:20:37,820
But let me tell you, Mr. Huang,

405
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:39,980
if Fengyang Mine really closes down,

406
00:20:39,980 --> 00:20:41,060
I'll have to come work for you.

407
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:42,540
You'll have to keep me fed.

408
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:44,140
Stop joking.

409
00:20:44,140 --> 00:20:45,260
I just got out of prison.

410
00:20:45,260 --> 00:20:47,020
I can't even feed myself.

411
00:20:47,020 --> 00:20:48,540
You're still a big player,
even on your last legs,

412
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:49,660
you're doing better than I do.

413
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:50,620
Anyway, I'm counting on you.

414
00:20:50,620 --> 00:20:51,860
Fine, we'll talk about it then.

415
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:53,190
- So it's a deal.
- Go on back.

416
00:20:53,260 --> 00:20:54,260
I'm off.

417
00:20:54,260 --> 00:20:55,140
Go.

418
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:22,220
Is watching me pee that interesting?

419
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,180
What is wrong with you?

420
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:32,060
I'm talking to you!

421
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:34,620
What is wrong with you?

422
00:21:34,620 --> 00:21:35,620
Who do you think you are?

423
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,340
Who is it?

424
00:21:47,740 --> 00:21:48,580
Huo Kaiming?

425
00:21:52,900 --> 00:21:53,860
You've lost your mind!

426
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:55,180
Help!

427
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:07,580
Help!

428
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:15,540
I'm sorry, man!

429
00:22:15,540 --> 00:22:17,860
I don't even want the money
you owe me anymore!

430
00:22:17,860 --> 00:22:19,580
Please, just let me go!

431
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:23,980
Help!

432
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:26,220
Go to heck!

433
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:29,220
Help!

434
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:37,140
Help!

435
00:22:39,740 --> 00:22:43,460
Help!

436
00:22:43,460 --> 00:22:45,660
What's going on?

437
00:22:45,660 --> 00:22:47,540
There's a fire over there! Someone help!

438
00:22:47,540 --> 00:22:48,980
Help!

439
00:22:53,660 --> 00:22:55,100
Quick, save him first!

440
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:20,420
(Emergency Department,
Outpatient Department)

441
00:23:25,220 --> 00:23:26,060
How is she, Doctor?

442
00:23:26,540 --> 00:23:27,820
It's just a bit of anemia.

443
00:23:27,820 --> 00:23:28,780
With her condition,

444
00:23:28,780 --> 00:23:29,820
anemia is quite normal.

445
00:23:30,740 --> 00:23:32,260
But she's never been like this before.

446
00:23:33,260 --> 00:23:34,780
The longer this illness drags on,

447
00:23:35,020 --> 00:23:36,780
the more severe
the complications will become.

448
00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:38,020
There's really no other way.

449
00:23:38,380 --> 00:23:40,500
Well, I'll prescribe some medicine first

450
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:41,860
to see if it can provide some relief.

451
00:23:41,860 --> 00:23:42,700
Thank you, Doctor.

452
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,780
Thank you, Doctor.

453
00:23:43,780 --> 00:23:44,620
Alright.

454
00:23:54,700 --> 00:23:55,540
I'm fine.

455
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:57,380
The doctor said

456
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,660
this is normal.

457
00:24:03,380 --> 00:24:04,540
I'm really okay.

458
00:24:05,820 --> 00:24:07,100
Don't worry.

459
00:24:07,100 --> 00:24:08,700
Go take care of your own business first.

460
00:24:12,780 --> 00:24:13,620
Alright.

461
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:15,100
I'll head back to the shop.

462
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:16,380
I'll come pick you up in a bit.

463
00:24:18,780 --> 00:24:19,620
Get some rest.

464
00:24:20,580 --> 00:24:21,500
Be safe on the road.

465
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:35,100
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

466
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:39,940
Dr. Liu?

467
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:41,060
Yes.

468
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,340
I wanted to ask,
since we've been on the list

469
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:43,340
for so many years now,

470
00:24:43,340 --> 00:24:45,010
is there still no news
on a kidney donor?

471
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:47,380
Right, I understand.

472
00:24:47,380 --> 00:24:49,020
But can you give me a rough timeframe?

473
00:24:51,300 --> 00:24:53,100
Yes, I understand your position,
but my girlfriend's body

474
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:54,100
can't wait much longer.

475
00:24:54,100 --> 00:24:55,620
She's been doing dialysis for so long.

476
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:00,900
I'm sorry.

477
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:02,700
I'm sorry, Doctor.

478
00:25:03,540 --> 00:25:04,980
I didn't mean to snap at you.

479
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:08,260
Right.

480
00:25:09,140 --> 00:25:10,220
Okay, I understand.

481
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:12,420
As soon as possible, please?

482
00:25:13,220 --> 00:25:14,160
Thank you for your help.

483
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:16,300
Goodbye.

484
00:25:20,700 --> 00:25:22,450
Is the Benz at the door yours?

485
00:25:22,450 --> 00:25:23,300
Yes.

486
00:25:23,300 --> 00:25:24,140
Why?

487
00:25:24,500 --> 00:25:25,540
Go check on it right now.

488
00:25:25,540 --> 00:25:26,580
Your car's been smashed.

489
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:28,700
Hurry.

490
00:25:29,300 --> 00:25:30,140
Hurry up.

491
00:25:30,510 --> 00:25:31,420
What happened?

492
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:33,180
I heard the sound of glass breaking.

493
00:25:33,180 --> 00:25:35,060
I came over and saw it like this.

494
00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:35,940
Go check it out.

495
00:25:37,780 --> 00:25:38,650
Take a look.

496
00:25:38,650 --> 00:25:39,740
Is anything missing?

497
00:26:26,860 --> 00:26:27,700
Who are you?

498
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:29,540
What did you do to Chen Hui?

499
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:49,100
What's going on?

500
00:26:49,820 --> 00:26:50,660
You can't park here.

501
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:51,860
Sir,

502
00:26:51,860 --> 00:26:52,700
you can't park here.

503
00:26:52,700 --> 00:26:53,540
Sir!

504
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:54,660
(Hemodialysis Room A)

505
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,360
Where's the patient in this bed?

506
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:01,460
I don't know.

507
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:02,300
She was just here.

508
00:27:07,580 --> 00:27:08,540
Songge,

509
00:27:08,540 --> 00:27:09,420
where did you go?

510
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:11,220
Chen Hui.

511
00:27:22,340 --> 00:27:23,180
Huo Kaiming.

512
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:26,860
You're living
quite a comfortable life, huh?

513
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:31,420
I'm living like a dog now.

514
00:27:34,020 --> 00:27:34,860
Where are you?

515
00:27:35,820 --> 00:27:36,900
Where did you take Songge?

516
00:27:37,740 --> 00:27:38,980
(Kill)
Oh, now you're worried?

517
00:27:40,820 --> 00:27:42,580
If you want to see your girlfriend,

518
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:43,820
do something for me first.

519
00:27:45,700 --> 00:27:46,540
Say it.

520
00:27:47,710 --> 00:27:48,900
You know Yang Baichun, right?

521
00:27:50,340 --> 00:27:51,180
I do.

522
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,100
Kill him.

523
00:27:55,820 --> 00:27:56,660
Otherwise,

524
00:27:58,380 --> 00:28:00,100
you'll never see your girlfriend again.

525
00:28:08,460 --> 00:28:09,300
Say something.

526
00:28:12,460 --> 00:28:13,820
I told you to speak!

527
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,580
Eight o'clock tonight.

528
00:28:18,860 --> 00:28:19,700
Liugou Coking Plant.

529
00:28:20,900 --> 00:28:21,740
You bring Songge,

530
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:23,860
and I'll bring Yang Baichun.

531
00:28:23,860 --> 00:28:25,420
Don't try to negotiate with me.

532
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:26,820
I want you to kill him!

533
00:28:26,820 --> 00:28:28,180
I want to see Songge first.

534
00:29:06,420 --> 00:29:09,180
(Fengyang Mine Workers' Hospital)

535
00:29:09,580 --> 00:29:11,420
Are you saying Huo Kaiming is back?

536
00:29:13,300 --> 00:29:14,540
Yes.

537
00:29:14,540 --> 00:29:15,660
Huo Kaiming said

538
00:29:15,660 --> 00:29:17,260
that this time,

539
00:29:17,260 --> 00:29:18,900
he doesn't plan on living.

540
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,260
He said

541
00:29:20,260 --> 00:29:22,020
he wants everyone who used to bully him

542
00:29:23,300 --> 00:29:24,820
to be buried with him.

543
00:29:27,220 --> 00:29:28,580
Then, why does he want to kill you?

544
00:29:29,500 --> 00:29:31,180
When he got into trouble at my pit,

545
00:29:32,580 --> 00:29:33,780
the woman he was with

546
00:29:34,820 --> 00:29:36,260
stole my money.

547
00:29:36,260 --> 00:29:37,860
I had my men

548
00:29:37,860 --> 00:29:38,900
beat up Huo Kaiming

549
00:29:39,660 --> 00:29:40,860
and told him to get

550
00:29:42,100 --> 00:29:42,940
my money back.

551
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:46,220
This is bad.

552
00:29:49,220 --> 00:29:50,450
- Hello.
- I'd like a room.

553
00:29:50,450 --> 00:29:51,300
A standard room.

554
00:29:53,140 --> 00:29:53,620
(Chen Hui)

555
00:30:07,300 --> 00:30:09,100
(Dad is calling)

556
00:30:09,460 --> 00:30:10,300
Dad.

557
00:30:10,300 --> 00:30:11,180
Hui,

558
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:12,020
where are you?

559
00:30:12,420 --> 00:30:13,620
I'm out taking care of something.

560
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:15,420
Hui, don't run around anymore.

561
00:30:15,420 --> 00:30:16,420
Limin

562
00:30:16,420 --> 00:30:18,080
is heading to your internet cafe.

563
00:30:18,210 --> 00:30:19,290
Go there and wait for him.

564
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:20,370
Dad, what I'm doing is important.

565
00:30:20,370 --> 00:30:21,300
I can't go back yet.

566
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:22,220
What could be so important?

567
00:30:22,220 --> 00:30:23,060
Listen,

568
00:30:23,220 --> 00:30:24,620
Huo Kaiming is back.

569
00:30:24,620 --> 00:30:25,460
He already put

570
00:30:25,460 --> 00:30:26,620
Mr. Huang in the hospital.

571
00:30:26,620 --> 00:30:28,260
You're in a very
dangerous situation right now.

572
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:29,100
Do you understand?

573
00:30:29,520 --> 00:30:31,500
Dad, whatever it is,
we'll talk when I get back.

574
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,020
You...

575
00:30:34,260 --> 00:30:35,100
This child...

576
00:30:35,380 --> 00:30:36,220
Speed up.

577
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:37,740
Is it ready?

578
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:44,140
Master.

579
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:44,980
Limin.

580
00:30:45,930 --> 00:30:46,810
Is Hui back yet?

581
00:30:46,810 --> 00:30:47,660
Hui isn't here.

582
00:30:47,660 --> 00:30:48,960
I called him, but he didn't pick up.

583
00:30:49,500 --> 00:30:50,340
Han,

584
00:30:50,820 --> 00:30:51,660
where did Songge go?

585
00:30:52,060 --> 00:30:53,420
She has dialysis today.

586
00:30:53,420 --> 00:30:54,340
She's not coming back.

587
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,300
You should close up this afternoon.

588
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:00,500
It's not safe for you to be here alone.

589
00:31:00,500 --> 00:31:01,340
Alright?

590
00:31:02,860 --> 00:31:03,700
Limin,

591
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:05,940
I'll go to the hospital for Songge.

592
00:31:05,940 --> 00:31:07,090
You guys go check her house.

593
00:31:07,100 --> 00:31:08,400
- Stay safe.
- Got it. Let's go.

594
00:31:08,500 --> 00:31:09,340
Hurry.

595
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,340
Hui.

596
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:33,620
Mr. Yang,

597
00:31:33,780 --> 00:31:35,340
where was the place

598
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,260
you mentioned last time?

599
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:39,580
Zhangtou Village.

600
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,420
You want to go?

601
00:31:40,860 --> 00:31:41,780
I've never seen it.

602
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:42,620
Just curious.

603
00:31:43,180 --> 00:31:44,020
Alright then.

604
00:31:45,340 --> 00:31:46,940
Come find me at 6:00 PM.

605
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:47,860
Got it, Mr. Yang.

606
00:31:47,860 --> 00:31:48,780
See you tonight.

607
00:31:48,780 --> 00:31:49,620
See you.

608
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:50,460
Sure.
